    "Once the compensation law is activated, K(t) adapts dynamically, leading to a further reduction in the steadystate error and achieving an approximate 31% decrease in the distribution error norm e T L 2 within 7.47 time units.",
    "C. Robustness evaluationWe numerically evaluated the robustness of the control algorithm against external disturbances.",
